  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="Aink14-kilavi">
        <p type="edition">talaimakaḷ puṇarcci vēṭkaiyaik kuṟippiṉāṉ uṇarnta tōḻi, ‘avaṉ koṭumai
          niṉaiyātu avaṉ mārpai niṉaintu āṟṟāyākiṉṟatu eṉṉai?’ eṉṟāṭku ‘avaṉ koṭiyaṉē yāyiṉum, avaṉ
          mārpu kuḷirnta tuyilac ceyyum iṉiya cāyalaiyuṭaittu, ātalāṟ kāṇ’ eṉac colliyatu.</p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"> </p>
      </div>

      <div xml:id="Aink14">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l> koṭippū vēḻan tīṇṭi yayala</l>
          <l> vaṭukkoṇ māattu vaṇṭaḷir nuṭaṅku</l>
          <l> maṇittuṟai yūraṉ mārpē</l>
          <l> paṉittuyil ceyyu miṉcā yaṟṟē.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
          <l> The chest of the man from the village by the ornate ghat—</l>
          <l rend="indent2"> where the sharp[-tipped] sprouts of the scarred mango trees</l>
          <l rend="indent2"> in the neighbourhood sway, touching the creeper flowers of wild cane—</l>
          <l> has the sweet grace that produces chilly sleep.</l>

        </lg>
      </div>
